}

text MossdeepCity_SpaceCenter_2F_Text_MaxieUseFuelToEruptVolcano {
    format("MAXIE: Fufufu… Since you're so curious, you deserve an explanation.\p We're going to jettison the entire load into MT. CHIMNEY!\p With GROUDON gone, we have no need for that slag heap of a mountain!\p So we'll use the fuel's power to make the volcano erupt!\p It will be savage!")
